				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Firstly, this is from someone who 2 boxes a mage/bard combo so I do know alot about how well a mage will fare against a bard.
<br />

<br />
The good news is that you have 10 levels on him and at 31 he doesn't have most of the nasty things bards get. Definitely open up with chains of pummice while sicking your pet. You need to strip his selos, this will absolutely cripple him at his levels. He will be constantly trying to recast selos while your pet hits him from behind. As long as you are willing to blow through 100pp in pummice you should do ok at your level. The chances of him having multiple instant clicks at 31 is pretty slim so I highly suggest you try this strategy.
<br />

<br />
Make sure you have a sow potion stacked deep in your buff stack. He won't have his dispell song (only self version) yet so the only way he can dispell you is via pummice. It is very important to have the runspeed spell on your pet and to keep selo stripped. If he gets a chance to run away and heal he will beat you eventually.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
