<br />

<br />
You have 10 levels on him...that makes all the difference in the world.  Just use an earth pet and try to malise him.  If you get malise on him he'll get rooted alot due to the level difference no matter what his resists are, and malise should screw up his resist songs due to the stacking issues.  Once rooted just throw Cinder bolts at him till dead...shouldn't take more than 5 at that level.  Also, summon up / get all the resist gear you can.  If you can get your MR over 100 he'll be cake.
<br />

