				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">ok this is coming from a old scholl sullon zeker. IF you can get him to fight indoors its all over just use your air pet for the stun because that stun will fuck him up.  But if it is outdoors what u have to do is get a malise on him because malise is poison based and he would need his 50+ song to get rid of that also he will try to kite ya pet and then run in and hit you probably which will fuck up ya spells.  what you need to do is make sure his selos is fucked up because he has shit dot songs he doesnt get a ok one that does 49 pvp dmg till bout 35 + i belive so that wont work good and since u got the lvls dont use a bolt unless he is in plain sight or else bolts wont hit they will run into anythign that is in the way liek a hill for example.  but if u malise him and root him u can just laugh.  use the earth pet if it is outside and summon weapons and armor for ya pet too and dont forget ya summons for ya especially the bracer which will help ya nukes iout by like 10%.  also if u can get that one health pot that is expensive but puts likes 1 dmg dot on u so that u will never get mezzed cause if he can mezz u and then kite ya pet out and mezz that thens its all over cause he can haste himself and fuck u up</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
